articles.author: Oliver Connolly
articles.title: NFL free agency: Jets are winners, Raiders are losers. The Broncos? Who knows? - The Guardian
articles.description: Building through free agency is typically seen as unwise, but several teams have addressed weaknesses this month without overpaying
articles.content:
Winners: Detroit Lions
With Aaron Rodgers ready to depart Green Bay, the Lions are in pole position to win the NFC North. They overhauled a shoddy secondary during the early days of free agency, add… [+10590 chars]
